---
import Container from "../layout/Container.astro";
---

<section class="bg-gray-50" aria-labelledby="offer-title">
    <Container>
        <h2 id="offer-title" class="m-0 mb-6 text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight relative pb-2 inline-block tracking-tight after:content-[''] after:absolute after:left-0 after:bottom-0 after:h-1.5 md:after:h-2 after:w-[58%] lg:after:w-[46%] after:bg-linear-to-r after:from-primary after:to-[#67a8ff] after:rounded-full after:shadow-[0_2px_6px_rgba(15,98,254,0.35)]">Naša Ponuka</h2>

        <div class="grid gap-4 md:gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 items-stretch" role="list">
            <article class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm flex flex-col group transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30" role="article">
                <figure class="m-0 h-40 lg:h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 italic border-b border-gray-100">
                    <img src="/images/offer/bytove-domy.jpg" alt="Bytové domy" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="p-4 lg:p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2.5">
                    <h3 class="m-0 text-[1.05rem] font-bold leading-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Bytové Domy</h3>
                    <p class="m-0 text-[#374151] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Komplexná revitalizácia bytovách domov - izolácia základov a spodnej stavby,
                        izolácia obvodového plášťa, opravy a izolácie striech.
                    </p>
                    <a class="mt-auto self-start inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white no-underline rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-[#0353e9]" href="#">Zistiť viac</a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm flex flex-col group transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30" role="article">
                <figure class="m-0 h-40 lg:h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 italic border-b border-gray-100">
                    <img src="/images/offer/balkony.jpg" alt="balkóny" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="p-4 lg:p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2.5">
                    <h3 class="m-0 text-[1.05rem] font-bold leading-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Balkóny</h3>
                    <p class="m-0 text-[#374151] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Rekonštrukcie, opravy a zateplenie balkónov bytových domov. Podkládky dlažby,
                        montáž a dodávka zábradlia alebo presklenia balkónov.
                    </p>
                    <a class="mt-auto self-start inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white no-underline rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-[#0353e9]" href="#">Zistiť viac</a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm flex flex-col group transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30" role="article">
                <figure class="m-0 h-40 lg:h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 italic border-b border-gray-100">
                    <img src="/images/offer/rodinne-domy.jpg" alt="rodinné domy" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="p-4 lg:p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2.5">
                    <h3 class="m-0 text-[1.05rem] font-bold leading-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Rodinné Domy</h3>
                    <p class="m-0 text-[#374151] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Výstavba rodinných domov na kľúč, rekonštrukcie, zateplenie, fasády, okná,
                        dvere. Komplexná revitalizácia rodinných domov.
                    </p>
                    <a class="mt-auto self-start inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white no-underline rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-[#0353e9]" href="#">Zistiť viac</a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm flex flex-col group transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30" role="article">
                <figure class="m-0 h-40 lg:h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 italic border-b border-gray-100">
                    <img src="/images/offer/zavesne-balkony.jpg" alt="závesné balkóny" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="p-4 lg:p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2.5">
                    <h3 class="m-0 text-[1.05rem] font-bold leading-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Závesné Balkóny</h3>
                    <p class="m-0 text-[#374151] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Realizujeme unikátnym systémom závesné balkóny pre bytové domy. Závesné
                        balkónové systémy - naša špecializácia.
                    </p>
                    <a class="mt-auto self-start inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white no-underline rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-[#0353e9]" href="#">Zistiť viac</a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm flex flex-col group transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30" role="article">
                <figure class="m-0 h-40 lg:h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 italic border-b border-gray-100">
                    <img src="/images/offer/strechy.jpg" alt="strechy" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="p-4 lg:p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2.5">
                    <h3 class="m-0 text-[1.05rem] font-bold leading-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Strechy</h3>
                    <p class="m-0 text-[#374151] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Izolácie, zateplenie a rekonštrukcie plochých striech bytových domov.
                        Výstavba všetkých typov striech bytových a rodinných domov.
                    </p>
                    <a class="mt-auto self-start inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white no-underline rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-[#0353e9]" href="#">Zistiť viac</a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm flex flex-col group transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30" role="article">
                <figure class="m-0 h-40 lg:h-44 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 italic border-b border-gray-100">
                    <img src="/images/offer/ostatne.jpg" alt="ostatné" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="p-4 lg:p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2.5">
                    <h3 class="m-0 text-[1.05rem] font-bold leading-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Ostatné</h3>
                    <p class="m-0 text-[#374151] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Ponúkame samozrejme omnoho viac a to napríklad rekonštrukcie bytov, pokládky
                        dlažby, budujeme cesty a chodníky. Kontakujte nás!
                    </p>
                    <a class="mt-auto self-start inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white no-underline rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-[#0353e9]" href="#">Zistiť viac</a>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>

